profile_positions.description:
Working in Well Completions Section, involved with research in sand consolidation, gravel packing, horizontal wells, slimhole completions, novel expandable devices, plugging systems and well remediation.
Responsible for planning and carrying out sand control field trials in Nigeria, North Sea, Netherlands and Brunei; 
Co-ordinating and supervising sand consolidation and gravel pack laboratory work; 
Supporting developments on horizontal well technology for unconsolidated reservoirs; 
Completions advisor for slimhole wells. Regularly gave training courses on Sand Control, Water Shut-Off and Horizontal Well Technology on Phase 1, 2 & 3 courses at Noordwijkerhout and in Brunei and Nigeria.
